{"tid":1353143,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"727急需不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T02:54:13.000Z","uid":131122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1ccfb2db67aa36ab9fe5e5b8233e0c29045df1","tid":1353143,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講直衝南邊圍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今次係反警黑勾結同要求警隊改革既好機會</span></span><br />\n不反對通知書可以有個確定地點時間<br />\n出邊有人九點有人十點有人十一點亂到七彩<br />\n同埋大家記住一定要將五大訴求既獨立調查委員會加入今次既遊行<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">淨係掛住報仇唔會贏得戰爭<br />\n要好好利用今次既憤怒<br />\n係元朗將矛頭指番落警隊</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4d0d75a50e312370475cbeabcdf28a7e741fa37","tid":1353143,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:07:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c45e422fc2ddf847cdf47e2aea3f45fb04ced3f4","tid":1353143,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">憤怒都要好好引導呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"9e34bd7b73de3bcd0a6152a50946c250a1573ee7","tid":1353143,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔撚係你想報仇就只掛住勇武<br />\n暴力背後既理念係人畜之別呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"0630663cf488c2780d95cc839e1adcaec6f31e07","tid":1353143,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:09:14.000Z","msg":"大家要去都一定要有遊行"},{"pid":"5198ead8f85afa25413c919552c24f8eb0a0d9dd","tid":1353143,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:09:30.000Z","msg":"打倒白色恐怖！"},{"pid":"8a16f56cb7763a2da33540035d79fb842c917c17","tid":1353143,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"改革警隊！！！"},{"pid":"6d307fb8da1f8eb44315d6c91b6fe9ab